description: The Fund employs a passive management – or indexing – investment approach, through physical acquisition of securities, and seeks to track the performance of the Bloomberg EM USD Sovereign + Quasi-Sov Index (the “Index“).The Fund invests in a representative sample of bonds included in the Index in order to closely match the Index’s capital and income return.The Index measures the performance of a broad spread of US dollar denominated bonds issued by emerging market governments and public bodies.Bonds in the Index have maturities of greater than one year and no credit rating constraints.To a lesser extent the Fund may invest in similar types of bonds outside the Index.
name: Vanguard USD Emerging Markets Government Bond UCITS ETF (USD) Distributing
